Package: libtree-sitter-c
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
Description: C grammar for tree-sitter
 tree-sitter-c is a C language grammar for tree-sitter. It enables syntax
 highlighting, structural editing, incremental parsing, and code analysis in
 editors and tools.
 .
 This package contains the shared library.

